# Internal-only documentation lives in the sibling folder outside this repo.
# Never commit it.
../internal-dev-docs/
internal-dev-docs/

# Screenshot evidence captured by Sol and Rook during PR review — not committed
# by default. PR-embed attachment subfolders are explicitly allowed so the
# images referenced from PR descriptions resolve from the repo. We use
# `screenshots/*` (not `screenshots/`) so the negation can re-include
# specific subdirectories — git cannot re-include a file under an
# entirely-excluded parent directory.
screenshots/*
!screenshots/pr-*-attachments/
!screenshots/pr-*-attachments/**
